column5: Where is this lake located? What are some of the nicer resorts on the lake? Can you bring your own boat or are the roads too rough on the trailer? Thanks for the info, sounds like a GREAT place to go for a vacation. Marty
Give me a e-mail and I will give you my thoughts on Kashabowie
